  "description": "Tide in auto-filter mode at 0.7 Hz creates a rhythmic undertow — the reverb tails get pulled through a resonant filter sweep that has nothing to do with the engine's internal modulation. Fathom compresses the burst of Tide's filter peaks so the undertow feels submerged rather than exposed.",
